snippet.textDisplay:
I had a gasp of delight and joy to see the brood, cozy and safe, in the Phoenix Empire's new tunnels. Thank you, as always, for sharing their journey with us!

Some additional name suggestions (though I'm super into István Baráth's "Tower of Hestia" idea as well):
- The Kindled Kingdom
- The Solarium
- The Temple of Pele (Hawaiian goddess of volcanoes and fire)
- Sunrise Spire (representing the sun rising on this new empire!)
- Hestia's Hearth (a variation on István's great idea)
